### Project Overview:  \
The TempoLabs AI editor project is a software solution for inventory management, designed to streamline tracking, sales, and financial operations. It offers real-time inventory updates, stock alerts, barcode scanning, and multi-location support, with role-based access and reporting capabilities.\
\
### Feature List:  \
\
1. **Inventory Tracking**  \
   - Track product quantities in real-time.  \
   - Add, update, or remove items easily.  \
   - Categorize items by type, brand, or location.  \
\
2. **Stock Alerts**  \
   - Notify users when stock levels fall below set thresholds.  \
   - Allow customization of minimum stock levels for each item.  \
\
3. **Barcode/QR Code Scanning**  \
   - Enable quick updates by scanning items.  \
   - Generate barcodes for new products.  \
\
4. **Sales and Purchase Tracking**  \
   - Record sales and purchases.  \
   - Automatically update inventory levels when items are sold or restocked.  \
\
5. **Income and Expense Tracking**  \
   - Track revenue from sales and business expenses.  \
   - Display net profit (income minus expenses) in a simple dashboard.  \
\
6. **User Roles and Permissions**  \
   - Create roles like Admin, Manager, and Staff.  \
   - Admins: Full access to all features.  \
   - Managers: Limited access (view reports, update stock).  \
   - Staff: Basic access (scan items, record sales).  \
\
7. **Reporting**  \
   - Generate reports on stock levels, sales trends, low-stock items, income, and expenses.  \
   - Export reports to PDF or Excel.  \
\
8. **Multi-Location Support**  \
   - Track inventory across multiple stores or warehouses.  \
   - Transfer stock between locations.}